      "raw_text": "One of the city's dad\" bills.\nwhich 1t is up to the new admins\ntration to straighten out, is the SIG\nbill for meals at the Club cafe for\npolicemen during the demonstra-\nton by union sympathizers against\nthe Washington Water Power Co,\nThe policemen were authorized to\neat at the Club on account of it's\nclose proximity to the scene of the\ndisturbances. The bill has not been\npaid, 1t was authorized by ex-Chief\nOF Police Waller.\n\n\nThe old city council did not take\nkindly to the payment of it. but\nwanted the men as individuals to\nsettle for what they ate."
